Title: 'Trip of Haridwar. '
DateModified: '2019-02-26'
DatePublished: '2019-02-26'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/trip-of-haridwar
SetInCountry: India
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Gavrav  Pratap Singh
AuthorCountry: India
Text: "Hamara safar suru hota Hh.. Lucknow se.. Pehli baar may uttar pradesh chod\
  \ ke jammu ke liye nikla tha.mere sath mere dad the Aur dadi ji.. Hum log Lucknow\
  \ se train se nikalte Hh.. Aur such pucho tho may bhot khus tha.. Because Mayne\
  \ kabhi pahaad nhi dekhe the. Jub ki mujhe neture se bachpan se hi bhot lagaaw tha..\
  \ May apne art ki copy me aksar pahaad, jharne Aur janglo ka hi penting krta tha..\
  \ An khusi Aur bhi thi ki papa ke sath pehli baar kahi ja raha hu\U0001F60A. Wayse\
  \ ghumne ka maza tho tabhi Hh jub mom or dad sath ho.. Kyu ki money ki koi problem\
  \ nhi hoti hh\U0001F61C. Train late Night me thi tho hum log so gye seet milte hi.morning\
  \ me papa ne jub uthaya tho hum log haridwar pahoch chuke the. Jub Mayne apni khidki\
  \ kholi tho may khusi se jhum utha. Kyu ki train pahado ke bich se gujar rahi thi.\
  \ Such pucho tho may pehli baar itna khus huwa tha. Train se dekhne par charo tarf\
  \ hare hare ped, jhadiya, jharne. Sub man ko bhot lubha rahe the, dekh ke Aysa lag\
  \ rha tha jyse Mayne koi bhot Badi jeet hasil Kar li ho. Thodi hi der me haridwar\
  \ satetion aaya hum log gadi se utre Aur riksa kiya, haridwar me bus Ganga ke hi\
  \ bare me suna tha. Jub ki haridwar ki market bhi bhot achi lag rahi thi. Hum logo\
  \ ne Hotel me samaan rakha.aur thoda aaram kiya but mera man bus Ganga ko dekhne\
  \ ke liye hi paresaan tha. Mayne papa ko Ganga me nahane ke liye manaya. Papa maan\
  \ bhi gye. Phir hum market ke Undar se. Ganga river ki taraf badhne lage. Jayse\
  \ jayse may. Ganga ki taraf badh rha tha mere dil ki dhadkane bhi khusi se badh\
  \ rahi thi. Thodi dur chalne par hi Ganga dikhne lagi. Jyse jyse Aage badhe dur\
  \ dur tak pani hi pani Aur bich me chote chote tappu. Aysa nazara tha ki ise hamesa\
  \ ke liye khud me sameetne ka man kar rha tha. Aur jub Nirmal Ganga ke dudh jyse\
  \ pani me suraj ki kirne padne lagi tho.. Pani sone jaysa chamkne laga. Yeh subeh\
  \ ka drisy bhot hi aatulniye tha.Ganga me nahane ke baad body tho fully relaxe ho\
  \ gai thi. But ik baat hh jo maza mujhe Ganga me nahane me aaya wo maza duniya ka\
  \ koi bhi swimming pool nhi de sakta. Kapde pahen ke baad may Aur papa hotel chal\
  \ diye. Hotel pahoch Kar bus Khane me hi man laga tha. Thodi der Khana aaya. Ghi\
  \ lagi hui roti Aur paneer ki sabji. Waah Kya swad tha yar. Aj bhi mujhe wo Khana\
  \ bhulaya nhi ja rha. Thoda aaram karke hum log market ghumne ke liye nikle. Market\
  \ me Kapde kaffi saste the Aur garm Kapde tho bhot hi saste the. Papa ne apne liye\
  \ jacket li Mayne apne liye awetar liya. Dadi ke liye saal li gai. Jayse jayse saam\
  \ ho rahi thi market me bish badhti hi ja rahi thi. Thode hi der me saam ho gai\
  \ hum log ko Ganga ki aarti dekhni thi jo ki pure word me bhot hi femas Hh. Log\
  \ kehte Hh haridwar jao aur Ganga aarti nhi dekha tho samjho kuch nhi dekha. Hotel\
  \ me samaan rakh kw hum log ghaat ki taraf badhe.. Lekin aarti start ho rahi thi.\
  \ Aur hum logo ko  kaffi piche jageh mili. Jivan me pehli baar Mayne itni badi aarti\
  \ nhi dekhi thi. Pandit ji dono hatho aarti pakad kar ghuma rahe the. Aur ghat se\
  \ bus.. Ganga aarti ki guj sunai pad rahi thi. Har koi hatho ko utha ke aarti gane\
  \ me saravor tha. Aarti ki lapte pani me padne se pani sone ke jayse chamak raha\
  \ tha. Aysa drisy tha ki har koi is drisy ko apne mobli Aur camera me sajoye ja\
  \ rha tha. Lagbhag 1 ghante ke baad aarti khatam hui.. Aur sabhi logo ne Ganga ke\
  \ jaikare lagaye. Aur chalne lage. Phir may Aur papa bhi hotel ki taraf nikal pade.\
  \ Aur dinner karke so gye. Morning me hamari train thi.\nAj 2saal baad bhi haridwar\
  \ dil aur dimaak se nikla nhi Hh."
